external_knowledge:
- "excelling" implies achieving a high rank and accumulating points;
- "more than a couple" means more than two times;
- "top-ten spot" means achieving a rank less than or equal to 10.

- "ventured into" refers to participating in;
- "more than one competition" refers to having participated in more than one tournament;
- "never clinched the top spot" means never achieved the first rank.

sql:
SELECT athlete_id, tournament_id, rank_change 
FROM athlete_ranks 
WHERE athlete_id = 1 AND tournament_id = 0;
